(28, '0', '他35岁，娶了死了丈夫的女人，结果竟然是这样.', '<p style=""><strong style=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 16px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="main" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 2px 2px 2px 6px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; border: 0px; border-top-left-radius: 2em; border-bottom-left-radius: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(0, 187, 236);"><span style="background-image:url(http://www.lieqicun.com/admin/neirong/pp.php)" width="1" height="1"></span><img data-ke-src="http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201311/d1cb6b2d4d3843d8ad8e77a79a337039.gif" data-ratio="0.5" data-w="22" class="" width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/lwpA0S3ABibYv65bp2tNPlaGadfh5R0SWct1ictXhv60pAqGxOPsFyagneqoILzbkrCkhrVhbicic62SM2ndoZ865A/0/mmbizgif?tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">提示</strong>：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">点击<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">↑</span></strong>上方</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">"FBI机密档案</span></span><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">"</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">关注我！</span></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n<p style=""></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13.3333339691162px; line-height: 21.1111125946045px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section title="" class="135bg" data-original-title="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 30px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); width: 667.77px; color: inherit; min-height: 300px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: url(http://img.hb.aicdn.com/35f9a85f859953cbf48b15d4c2f9ba6fd7716db15e1d-AyBgcC_fw658); background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat;"><section class="135editor" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 30px 0px; padding: 30px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.298039);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/mbEIo6ytubyP4YtzRAibU4sIbSibj43Fsnz03FfnicgOaDoiaRCeaAW7hLic3uD8hP9yJ0BuMjQ11oX8RA4NQyXz3jA/640?wxfrom=5&amp;tp=webp" data-ratio="0.9352331606217616" data-w="386" width="auto" suffix_360="37dda2b2431e40b5d8367994591d7444" suffix_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/mbEIo6ytubyP4YtzRAibU4sIbSibj43Fsnz03FfnicgOaDoiaRCeaAW7hLic3uD8hP9yJ0BuMjQ11oX8RA4NQyXz3jA/640&amp;wxfrom=5"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13.3333339691162px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有一位李大爷，由于家里太穷，到了35岁时才与本村一位死了丈夫的女人结了婚，婚后生下一个儿子，取名晚生。李晚生读书很聪明，尽管他高中毕业正赶上知识青年上山下乡。他是农村人，不用上山下乡了，直接回乡接受贫下中农的再教育。他回家锻炼了一个月，被大队干部推荐到大队小学任教。在小学干了两年，又被大队干部推荐上了大学。</span></p>\n<p><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13.3333339691162px; line-height: 21.1111125946045px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13.3333339691162px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李大爷没有想到自己三十多岁喜得贵子，李家坳大队第一个上大学的人竟是自己的儿子。有很多人羡慕他，儿子大学一毕业，就拿铁饭碗，将来在城里安家了，再将老父亲接到城里享清福。在李家坳也是头一个。夫妻俩见到恭维的人乐得嘴快合不拢了。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生大学毕业后，被分配到本县财政局工作，半年之后，谈了一女朋友，她姓方名秀英，家在农村，大学毕业后，分配在县工商局工作。一年之后，两人结婚了。 一次，李晚生的父亲进城了，找到了儿子的家里，儿媳见公公第一次上门，知道有事，不然不会找上门的。问道：“爸，您今天是第一次上门，一定是有事，什么事，您说，我和您的儿子，一定给您解决。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“既然你问了，我就不绕弯子，最近家里手头没有钱，现在正是插秧的季节，请人帮工，买化肥都需要钱，我今天来就是要点钱回去，解决燃眉之急。” “您托人捎信说一下，需要多少，我们将钱带回去，您就不必亲自上门，这钱我得跟您的儿子商量一下。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">方秀英等到丈夫一进家门，没等丈夫跟公公打招呼，就拉着他进了房间，你的父亲来了，我离不开身去买菜，家里只有青菜，你爸不是贵客，招待好不好，他老人家不会计较的。他今天来是要钱的，回去支付插秧的费用，你说给多少合适？”“你说给多少？”“50元应该够了吧。”“你就给50元吧。少了，父亲会想办法的。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">方秀英简单的炒了几个粗菜，招待了公公。饭后，方秀英掏出50元钱，交给公公，说：“这50元钱支付插秧费应该够了吧。”李大爷接过钱，什么也没有说，闷闷不乐地回家了。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">只过了两天，方秀英的娘找上门来，方秀英一见娘上门，便关切地问道：“妈，您今天是不是来要钱的？”她的娘点了一下头。她吩咐娘在家看好家，她急忙去去买鱼、买肉，买鸡蛋……<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生下班回家时，她拉开门时，说：“我妈来了，你快去打招呼，别怠慢了老人家。她今天也是来要钱的，你说给多少合适？”“你说给多少？”“最少500元才行。”“你就给500元吧。”方秀英的娘拿了500元钱，高高兴兴地回去了。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">方秀英怀孕了，将这一好消息告诉了丈夫，问他：“你是希望我生个儿子，还是生个女儿？”他告诉妻子，最好是生个女儿。“你这人真怪，希望我生女儿，生女儿有什么好？”李晚生什么没有说。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一转眼，方秀英怀胎8个月，她回到娘家养胎待产，临走时，李晚生郑重告诉妻子：“你如果生的是女儿，要及时告诉我。如果生的是儿子，就不必告诉我了，最好将儿子送给别人。”“你这人是怎么啦？为什么不喜欢儿子？”他没有回答妻子的话。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一天，李晚生接到丈母娘捎来的口信，说方秀英喜得一千金，李晚生一听高兴地跳了起来。他向单位领导请了假，告知自己的老婆生了女儿，他要去丈母娘家看望女儿。领导向他恭贺，也批了他的假。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生买了十六只鸡，300个鸡蛋，还有许多补品，挑着一担花钱买的东西，高高兴兴地去了丈母娘家。进门后，将东西放在厨房的饭桌上，顾不得喝丈母娘送上手的糖水，走进房门。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他来到妻子的床前，二话不说，掀开盖在妻子身上的被子，“你让我看看到底是女儿，还是儿子。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“你看了保证高兴。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生抱起孩子，放在被子上，迫不及待地揭开裹在孩子身上的衣物，一看不是女儿，生气地吼道：“你们为什么骗我？秀英你难道忘了我曾经说过，生儿子就不用告诉我的话吗？”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生说完，走出房间，拿起厨房饭桌上的东西就走，并说：“这儿子我不要，你们爱送谁就送给谁。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他的丈母娘见女婿真的生气了，拉住女婿的手，说：“人家生儿子是特别高兴，你是什么原因要将儿子送给别人？今天你必须说明原因，你才可以走出这屋子。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生站住了，说：“我的父母生下我，为了我读书、上大学，结婚，掏空了家底。可我自参加工作以来，逢年过节回去总是两手空空的，父母过生日也没有为老人家花过一分钱。自从我结婚以来，我的父亲在万般无奈的情况下，上门向我要了一次钱，回去支付插秧的费用，您的宝贵女儿只给50元钱，这50元能干啥用？我的父亲拿着50元钱，含着眼泪离开时，说过一句话‘生儿子有啥用？’当时我一听父亲的话，我的心里在流血。您说我要儿子有啥用？”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“晚生，我不知道自己的女儿对待你的父母没有孝道，只怪我和她的父亲没有教育好，请你原谅我们，是我养的孩子没有家教。你要走，我没有脸面留下你，你就将你的妻子带走吧，别让她留在我家。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他的丈母娘松开手，走进房间，来到女儿的床前，掀开被子，气愤地说：“你抱着你的儿子给我滚出去，我没有你这样的女儿。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“妈，我错了，我以后决心改，一定好好地孝敬我的公婆，您就让我做完月子再走吧，求求您留下我！”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李晚生听了妻子和丈母娘的对话，见自己的目的已达到了，放下东西，走进房间，说：“妈，您别生气，您的女儿认错了，您就给她机会吧，留下她。她母子俩吃的、喝的、还有您的护理工钱，我会一分不少算清楚的。”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“只要她说话算数，留下她可以，护理费我可不敢要。”李晚生留下照料妻子，直到假期满了才走。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">父母一路养育我们长大，给予了我们许多，我们逐渐有了自己的思想，自己的思维方式，这时候，我们不是应该胡思乱想，而是要好好想想父母这些年来对我们的养育之恩，虽说现在孝顺父母也被写进了法律，但真的的孝顺父母不是要法律法规来要求的，而是自觉的。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们一天天长大，父母一天天变老，逐渐长出了白头发，以前小时候不懂事，看见父母的白头发只会笑哈哈的说你们老了，现在想起来，父母的沧桑、辛苦，都是为了我们子女的幸福，为了给我们一个好的环境，我们长大了，更不应该让父母操心了，我们要做力所能及的事，帮父母分担分担，减轻父母肩上的重担，像回家洗碗，扫地，给父母捶捶背，洗衣服等等我们都能做到，能做到的我们就应该积极去做，让父母休息一下。希望大家有空多在家陪陪父母。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当你读完本篇文章时，你有两个选择： 1、你可以将它传扬出去，传播一些积极正面的信息，让世间多一点爱。 2、你也可以根本不去理会它，就像你从未看见一样。</span></span></p></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>↓↓↓↓点击</strong></span><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);">阅读原文</span><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">关注看下集</span></strong></span></p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/THdGeztIeOcib5qwrSczsARWf4CHSbrejVzU9udAWT5SvyffAHrBQOZpVnd7yu7x9gzUHaGibErs3HmOBsBBNQoA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '34', '28', '-1', 0.05, '2015-08-02');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `top`, `title`, `content`, `pic`, `type`, `pv`, `pv_max`, `money`, `day`) VALUES
(29, '0', '“老公~我要...”“老婆，我真不行了…”能看懂的都不是一般人！', '<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457obpB4cXa9HLhyl0UrDcVvdic1ic0VNLIEeY8ZSRwXibO7l5XE4opldpYw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.46875" data-w="480"><br></p>\n<blockquote class="wxqq-borderTopColor wxqq-borderRightColor wxqq-borderBottomColor wxqq-borderLeftColor" style="padding: 15px; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border-top-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-style: dashed; border-color: rgb(86, 235, 0);">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457el6laZrJ7fiaDRmPuq2tKUEEhDaubAz2QXku2KiaF2RlT7WZ5JwMAbEQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6675" data-w="400"><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: tahoma; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">1.看中一台电脑，需要9000元。他每月的收入只有2000.老婆对他说，你疯了，你买了就离婚。他问我怎么办。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">我说，你配不上那个电脑。连自己喜欢的东西都没勇气去争取你将来在社会上还能混成啥样？他咬咬牙买了。为了还债他开始不停的兼职。终于在一个月内还清了所有的余款。他的妻子并没有因为他的疯狂而离开他。他的妻子把他带进了车市，说：老公，我们贷款买了这辆宝马吧。他一开始吓死了。以为老婆是疯了。1年后他还清了宝马的贷款。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】你连追求自己喜欢的事物与人的勇气都没有，你注定是个失败者。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style=""><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457Pp9xqL0HRxvZkwgz41azxibI1hpEvg3MqSB79oAXy6iaw1FiaWibegAAUQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.7489361702127659" data-w="470"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">2.两马各拉一货车。一马走得快，一马慢吞吞。于是主人把后面的货全搬到前面。后面的马笑了：“切！越努力越遭折磨！”谁知主人后来想：既然一匹马就能拉车，干嘛养两匹？最后懒马被宰掉吃了。这就是经济学中的懒马效应。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】让人觉得你可有可无，你被踢开的日子就不远了。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457WMj63gZheWtTlPYBZ9GMeHqsqUxRv7iaBwNoK4r6nxr5ibRgdCMYBDLg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6574468085106383" data-w="470"></p></section><section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">3.夜市有两个面线摊位。摊位相邻、座位相同。一年后，甲赚钱买了房子，乙仍无力购屋。为何？原来,乙摊位生意虽好，但刚煮的面线很烫，顾客要15分钟吃一碗。而甲摊位，把煮好的面线在冰水里泡30秒再端给顾客，温度刚好。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】为客户节省时间，钱才能进来快些。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457EKDxkdA8UKe2OCRRhltKh3levbwkicwwkK9ln85H2ricXavkyt4k7HaA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6391982182628062" data-w="449"></p></section><section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">4.一禅师见一蝎子掉到水里，决心救它。谁知一碰，蝎子蛰了他手指。禅师无惧，再次出手，岂知又被蝎子狠狠蛰了一次。旁有一人说：它老蜇人，何必救它？禅师答：蜇人是蝎子的天性，而善是我的天性，我岂能因为它的天性，而放弃了我的天性。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】我们的错误在于，因为外界过多地改变了自己。</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/kHIx3xXM5YiclwXCPurEaSE5LlrQgcJWVFnKRhMpNSHCAicgwMox1Sxm1uODn6zIqAMWDfIBhL3ficaRAI7TNiaiacA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" data-ratio="0.8170212765957446" data-w="470"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">5.曼德拉曾被关压27年，受尽虐待。他就任总统时，邀请了三名曾虐待过他的看守到场。当曼德拉起身恭敬地向看守致敬时，在场所有人乃至整个世界都静了下来。他说：当我走出囚室，迈过通往自由的监狱大门时，我已经清楚，自己若不能把悲痛与怨恨留在身后，那么我仍在狱中。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】原谅他人，其实是升华自己。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/kHIx3xXM5YiclwXCPurEaSE5LlrQgcJWVwEnlM1GdTjQs8KfqdGuDicWibUJSUGiad6YrribkhGmhAdmDbYMkeVSyaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" data-ratio="1.3340425531914895" data-w="470"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">6.有人问农夫：“种了麦子了吗？”农夫：“没，我担心天不下雨。”那人又问：“那你种棉花没？”农夫：“没，我担心虫子吃了棉花。”那人再问：“那你种了什么？”农夫：“什么也没种，我要确保安全。”</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】一个不愿付出、不愿冒风险的人，一事无成对他来说是再自然不过的事。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457QH9wiaYmSdvLampz3XJCLxMiaQHHVusn6EiahDrSsm5MWma5LicJM55QVg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5323275862068966" data-w="464" url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457QH9wiaYmSdvLampz3XJCLxMiaQHHVusn6EiahDrSsm5MWma5LicJM55QVg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" file_id="209710101" format="jpeg" source="lib" data-s="300,640"></p></section><section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">7.三人出门，一带伞，一带拐杖，一空手。回来时，拿伞的湿透了，拿拐杖的跌伤了，第三个好好的。原来，雨来时有伞的大胆地走，却被淋湿了；走泥路时，拄拐杖的莽撞地走，时常跌倒；什么都没有的，大雨来时躲着走，路不好时小心走，反倒无事。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】很多时候，我们不是败在缺陷上，而是败在优势里。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457cncU6B9gw9ZQCGqtVj2snPicLYYFfytCqpkCSJhhomjM1VsBCy1zq6w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5809312638580931" data-w="451"></p></section><section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">8.一个小镇中，一位商人开了一个加油站，生意特别好，第二个来了，开了一个餐厅，第三个开了一个超市，这片很快就繁华了。另一个小镇，一位商人开了一个加油站生意特别好，第二个来了，开了第二个加油站，第三个、第四个恶性竞争大家都没得玩。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】一味走别人的路，必将堵死自己的路。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/kHIx3xXM5YiclwXCPurEaSE5LlrQgcJWVCsXFSt9sicESSjfV5zhcJh9HoictIXKFUMRk0JrmPlTgLs0pcEQveEng/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" data-ratio="0.6111111111111112" data-w="468"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">9.一只乌鸦在飞行的途中碰到回家的鸽子。鸽子问：你要飞到哪？乌鸦说：其实我不想走，但大家都嫌我的叫声不好，所以我想离开。鸽子告诉乌鸦：别白费力气了！如果你不改变声音，飞到哪都不会受欢迎的。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】如果你希望一切，都能变得更加美好，就从改变自己开始。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY4579fhg9ibmzac6UdZYVx9RbXKPoibXUibz1zE1V61NQgm6olK77KlawCeGw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6921397379912664" data-w="458"></p></section><section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">10.一户人家有三个儿子，他们从小生活在父母无休止的争吵当中，他们的妈妈经常遍体鳞伤。老大想：妈妈太可怜了！我以后要对老婆好点。老二想：结婚太没有意思，我长大了一定不结婚！老三想：原来，老公是可以这样打老婆的啊！</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">【悟到】即使环境相同，思维方式不同，也会影响人生的不同。</span></strong></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/kHIx3xXM5YiclwXCPurEaSE5LlrQgcJWVjHJnvzcic2dchjLgnibgOgZ9lOJqHYnxHXPF0YgKpGtIemNndBMAmZ1A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" data-ratio="0.7510638297872341" data-w="470"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">11.小和尚负责清扫寺院落叶，每天要很长时间才能扫完。有人对他说：“你打扫前用力摇树，把落叶统统摇下来，明天就不用打扫了。”小和尚觉得很对，就高兴地照办了，可第二天院子里如往日一样满地落叶。无论你今天怎么用力，明天的落叶还是会飘下来。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【悟到】活在当下。</span></strong></span></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/kHIx3xXM5YiclwXCPurEaSE5LlrQgcJWVYonsUFEibJx0K1q2Q9uJvdchuEkMKQMHMOTwgFa2gicUJn1ZPR9BdMlg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5" data-ratio="0.7510638297872341" data-w="470"></p>\n<section class="135article"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;" data-id="29735" class="135editor"><section style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="50%" style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; height: 8px; margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; width: 50%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); padding: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="text-indent: 2em;" style="padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; margin: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">12.野猪和马一起吃草，野猪时常使坏，不是践踏青草，就是把水搅浑。马十分恼怒，一心想要报复，便去请猎人帮忙。猎人说除非马套上辔头让他骑。马报复心切，答应了猎人的要求。猎人骑上马打败了野猪，随后又把马牵回去，拴在马槽边，马失去了原先的自由。</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 17px; list-style: none; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, helvetica, arial; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, helvetica, arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【悟到】你不能容忍他人，就会给自己带来不幸。</span></strong></span></p></section><section data-width="65%" style="padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; width: 65%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-width="8px" style="margin: 0px auto 1px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJyxHU18DWgne4ibqgxEDRY457JmiaK2zT7tuuDMwnGYP0jacCriaLeDB5EN646AupFSbrBeKV9XWmv5icQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-w="480"><br></p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/d9iaByDnAJywicXrzCngSsJS7v0Uh75yv8doMFnib172ibYv2OVicCJCrmQ9IXXEuSt1m9g0pHYjzAhibxyEH5wKpD1g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '34', '50', '-1', 0.05, '2015-08-02');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `top`, `title`, `content`, `pic`, `type`, `pv`, `pv_max`, `money`, `day`) VALUES
(30, '0', '玩的就是智商！LOL十大致命陷阱', '<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRaPyOIA63NtjbEGEJNMyKce97Bu6mEiaA10HNbd8gnu8piaRO1boKyUOQ74Xgj7RlgtKZB9jmVzLVYw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.18972332015810275" data-w=""><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section data-id="undefined" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="border: 0px; font-size: 16.3636360168457px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><section style="display: inline-block; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><section style="display: inline-block; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><p style="word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: inherit;"><br></p></section><span style="background-color:rgb(235, 103, 148); border-radius:0.3em; box-shadow:rgb(16, 146, 113) 0.1em 0.1em 0.1em; color:rgb(255, 255, 255); display:inline-block; font-size:1em; font-weight:inherit; padding:0.3em; text-align:inherit; text-decoration:inherit">微信号：Miss_game</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="391" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 1.5em 1em 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(255, 179, 167); border-image-source: none; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.4; margin-left: -0.5em; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding: 0px;"><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 3px 8px; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(167, 23, 0); font-size: 1em; display: inline-block; -webkit-transform: rotateZ(-10deg); transform: rotate(-10deg); transform-origin: left center 0px; -webkit-transform-origin: 0% 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 179, 167);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255)">Miss</span></section></section><section class="135brush" data-style="line-height:24px;color:rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size:14px" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 22px 16px 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 179, 167); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; margin-top: -24px;"><p style="line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px;">    LOL不仅讲究操作，更讲究心理和计谋，玩的就是智商，下面就带大家看看游戏中有哪些致命的陷阱，一定要当心哦。</span></p></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.10-消失的视野</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRZ6dHDqG53j4fxQL1mbScxppncJj1E2WbjoZVg5nq0agkpfiaVKSjpNfIWAnISk2rFsgc2AS7o0Dibg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.67" data-w="500"><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">河道作为两方进攻的“小路”而向大家充分的展现了“眼位”的重要性，新版本中的螃蟹生死存亡更加牵绊了大小龙的命脉。在很多职业联赛里，往往是视野控制好的那一方有更好的表现，辅助打野双双眼石，各路又自己带真假眼，就是一门学问。在早期的比赛中，打野在河道草丛放了一个真眼，这对于中路和上下路也是个非常充足的防GANK保护，看清打野的动向，看清地图上各个英雄的动向，没有什么比明亮的视野更人放心的了。但是，一个消失视野的河道，一个消失视野的野区，你被对方盯上了，你的野被人家反了，你都一无所知。没有什么比企图单杀对手的时候，他的队友正在伺机捕获你的人头更可怕了。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.9-突然的进攻和突然怂了</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">当然双人路也会出现各种演，更不说单人路，把这种‘勇’和‘怂’展现的淋漓尽致。一个被你压着打的人突然勇了起来，一个压着你打的人突然让你收兵线了，这真的是不正常的，我们要去了解这种心理，也要反过来利用这种心理。比如锤石的灯笼唱空城计，比如中单一直被你压却突然贴着一边试图勾引你，一般来说，你都以为有人来了，其实就是利用了这种心理，来达到他发育的目的。你看到上路一个人突然和你拼了，你没视野，不知道他们打野是不是来了，正常 就怂一点，这样他们就又可以发育一波了。当然要虚虚实实的，有时利用这个‘勇’突然上前，和这个‘怂’突然的后撤，来勾引一些对你有想法红了眼的人，这些人就像喝高了二锅头一样，脑子处理不过来，就这样上来，被我们打野一起轮了他的菊。有时就要用这种方法来达到发育的目的，打野虽然没来，但我让你感觉他来了，有时也发信号打字让他真来，让对手不知道真假空城，对手就让你玩弄在股掌之间。</span></p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.8-人的本质就是贪婪的</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRZ6dHDqG53j4fxQL1mbScxp8usqwSGEJ1Y2nUInXicXPCVJtmswMPvhHRrTibtAEibKU4G0yMv9YAcqw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.614" data-w="500"><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">人性天生就是无限贪婪的，召唤师峡谷，这个充满壮烈争斗，智勇双伐之地，在它的历练下，学会到的也是人生的真谛。当你拼杀完了你的对线敌人，存下的一条兵线你是吃好还是不吃好？吃了，可以让自己小兵到他们塔下，使对方英雄吃不到经验。但吃了，对面的支援可是看着你这个残血，口水都流出来了！已经数不清多少低分局忽略队友发的信号--拼杀完残血快撤，敌方打野或者中MISS，就是因为贪几个兵，觉得清个兵有多久，结果倒是更快的回到了泉水 NO.7-全屏大招流。当敌方有全屏大招英雄时候，比如大家所熟悉的EZ,金克斯，炸弹人，寒冰等等等等，自己残血回家就得注意一下。你玩这些英雄的时候知道收残血的人头，对面当然也知道。首先要找一个敌方没视野的敌方，然后再考虑下自己回城的敌方是不是敌方可能放大的地方。比如塔下，如果是的话，就得换位置了。最后回城的时间里千万不要先点商店看装备，盯着对面可能会放大招的英雄，随时准备着看需不需要位移一下，安全第一。别不信邪，很多人都在这个时候栽了不知道多少次。</span></p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.6-僵持时对面先手英雄的跃跃欲试</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">大家常常发育到差不多的时期就要开始双方打团了，你看到一个石头人在你面前晃来晃去的时候就要想想，假如你是这个石头人，你会什么时候大，肯定要大到人多的地方或者主要输出脆皮的地方，你该用闪现躲就闪，多过关键的技能才有输出的环境可能。石头，皇子，雷欧娜，阿木木等这些都是开团的好手，但是你怎么也得打，到了后期这些强开英雄也不会变弱！你玩输出位置的时候尽量不要被大到，用技能用走位用闪现都可以保护自己，看到强开英雄心里要有压力，有了压力脑子才会清醒思路清晰。才会指引你作出正确的反应。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.5-喜欢一级团</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">在低分段一级团几乎把把都会出现，队友不会看小地图，不会管你是不是有队友挂机，直接就是跑到小龙河道处跟对面秀自己自信的走位。其实一级团在低分段没有任何好处，坏处更多。比如你家一级团赚了，梦幻开局，对面的往往会小心翼翼的认真游戏，自己家队友各种浪觉得自己优势大，往往一级团赢得被翻盘的更轻松。再比如你家一级团输了，低分段的喷子多，没有能力承受心理压力，就开始喷队友，开始送，开始对骂什么的，让你们直接一波一级决定了整局游戏的可玩性。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.4-不罢休的追击敌方残血</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRZ6dHDqG53j4fxQL1mbScxpWGhS4qhaGAibY2oBmuXib3D0Vz3TKJB6vXSZZYIzaaXwoyO3EzaH4SqA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.564" data-w="500"><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">我们经常能在低分段里看见，在一波成功的消耗后，留下了敌方剩下一丝血量逃离了自己的伤害范围之外。此时往往会很多人穷追不舍不愿意错过这个人头，却往往在两三个人追击对面一个残血的时候，换来的是进了对面赶来的支援圈套内，被秀的一脸。在没有视野的敌方，最好就是见好就收。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.3-进排位在5L自爆是DL（代练）的</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">早期的玩家都知道，S4之前说这话的可信度比较高。在这个新赛季开始，严打DL，来维护游戏平衡。所以现在敢自爆5L是DL的一般正常都是臭脾气的喷子，或者是父母惯坏了的小学生。起码现在我们都不会说自己是DL，因为在低分段喷子多，要么就喷起来，要么就信了。喷起来自然进去也很危险，他要是坑了就别玩了，喷到你家人去都会。还有就是信你是DL给你让位了，给低分段的人觉得这把我们可以抱大腿了，自己坑了都还有机会翻盘，但是！！！往往现在这种自爆DL的进去后不到三分钟比单杀几次后，要么喷打野不会，要么喷中单不懂游走，不玩了，挂机。勘称坑爹级别陷阱！所以排第三当之无愧。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.2-大龙毁一生！！！</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;">大家都知道这句话，也在各种比赛中看到了打大龙毁一生屡屡出现。而在低端局里打大龙却经常是可行的，因为那个地方一局下来几乎没有插过几个眼，而且低分段的人很少遇到会带占卜宝珠饰品的。我们在游戏里也经常会遇到在大龙处排除视野等埋伏，这时候看不到敌方的英雄大龙又没视野，最好不要自己一个人轻易过去作死，十有八九是一个大陷阱在等待着你去送死。可以学学职业赛里的组合，带个占卜宝珠打开视野看看对方是否真的在打大龙，避免全图摸黑脸探草丛的危险。</p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><section class="135article"><section data-id="44423" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:18px"><strong><span class="135brush" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="background:rgb(255, 159, 168); border-bottom:4px solid rgb(255, 124, 135); border-radius:3px; font-size:18px; line-height:36px; margin:0px 7px 11px 0px; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center">NO.1-敌方的复活基地</span></strong></span></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRZ6dHDqG53j4fxQL1mbScxpsBzbWFib1icAibJphp10kQ28rLdLbykeIobkjY2BibE5MPAkBAYBtD9zGg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5666666666666667" data-w="450"><br></p>\n<section class="135article"><section data-id="24" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135brush" style="margin: 3px; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">最后的最后，在一把游戏几乎没什么悬念的情况下，都可以在对方的复活基地门前装个B跳个舞什么的。但是假如在大后期阵容优势差不多的情况下，尤其是对面有牛头人，机器人，锤石之类的英雄，千万不要作死。小心人家把你送进去基地任你神装也是瞬间死亡，尤其是蛮王，基地掉的血蛮王大是无效的。要知道后期死一次复活时间70秒以上，如果不是优势非常大，小心一波让你笑不起来。<span style="font-size: 12px;">(图文来源TX)</span></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"></span></span></p>\n<section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 0px 0px -0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; border-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: inherit; -webkit-transform: rotateZ(-10deg); -webkit-transform-origin: 0% 100% 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Miss淘宝店</section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p>\n<p><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; white-space: normal; margin: -24px 0px 0px; padding: 22px 16px 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></span><span class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">外设</span>：<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">missgame</span>.taobao.com</section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">零食</span>：<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">missfood</span>.taobao.com</section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">男装</span>：<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">chuanmiss</span>.taobao.com</section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">鞋子</span>：<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">maimiss</span>.taobao.com</section></span></section></p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRaPyOIA63NtjbEGEJNMyKcexb1FQZEw4h7gftl7wC0DyqCW9aHhor3DXcCa8bbgmTvk45lqcxoE5A/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.18972332015810275" data-w=""><br><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRbPjuzm4qUuV8GTNHib29oyTqibAaQAXXu5PYlNUym74EU7TY4cVCHByE77aAkcHN62tCGQkKfKjAHg/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="1.0666666666666667" data-w="180"><br><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.375px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(55, 74, 174);">Miss大小姐 / 合作邮箱：miss_game@qq.com</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E7CwT21rlRbro9SNEiaLxY5tZ6o65Mnt4kuPTMyAkFnibBjJdvzyBCYuwGxnl0a74GmJU8nJRb36VKW4aRibllibYg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '34', '49', '-1', 0.05, '2015-08-02');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `top`, `title`, `content`, `pic`, `type`, `pv`, `pv_max`, `money`, `day`) VALUES
(31, '0', '牙疼，也分8种疼法！严重程度大不同！', '<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xOKbSrIBGgib7B4xThEnaxkfzEGy58ZMjWic95f9PibGQo7SVJWicHAYAeT8cSficzezSyiaZdoiaeVPfKc2wdyl0GRjw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.3774703557312253" data-w=""><br></p>\n<p>本文发表于陈宁医生好大夫在线个人网站。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>俗话说“牙疼不算病，疼起来要人命”。那么，牙齿为什么会疼？是不是所有的牙疼都一样呢？你猜猜看——</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>下面揭晓答案——造成牙齿疼痛的原因，其实主要就是细菌感染牙髓或牙周组织，导致的炎症反应。不同时期的炎症阶段，牙疼的特点可是不一样的哦——</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;" data-original-title="" title="">1</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">冷热刺激疼，最佳治疗时期</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>牙髓感染初期会出现充血，这一阶段，牙齿一般无明显持续性疼痛。多数人只是感觉冷热刺激疼，而且很多还是“一过性”的敏感，说不上疼。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>但是，你如果忽视了这个阶段的不适感觉，那么很可能就错过了最佳治疗时期。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;" data-original-title="" title="">2</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">持续疼，睡觉更疼，炎症加重</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>随着炎症加重，牙髓开始出现浆液性渗出，期间牙齿中间的髓腔内部压力会逐渐随炎症发展而急剧升高，从而造成神经疼痛（有点象家里用的压力锅啊）！</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>牙髓组织被细菌分解，变成流动性液体，此时牙齿会感觉到持续性的疼痛，再发展会出现跳疼（一蹦一蹦的）。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>此时的疼痛多伴随有体位性改变而疼痛程度的改变，并且多数是夜间加重。你感觉到的就是一到晚上想睡觉就疼，躺下就重，站起来就缓解。</p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xOKbSrIBGgib7B4xThEnaxkfzEGy58ZMjpEPtM32s9yLFOe6zUHAjffFwKdwJlGSmHbnxOiaMDEqF4x9O3pibyicQA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.0368663594470047" data-w="434"><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">3</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">冷水刺激不疼了，你危险了！</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>当炎症再发展，就会出现牙髓坏死，此阶段你会有一种奇怪的感觉：冷水刺激不疼了，倒觉得舒服，既而疼痛也不厉害了，牙根有点痒，还有人有胀的感觉，牙涨高的感觉，使劲咬牙时会很舒服。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>很高兴吗？告诉你——你危险了！</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>此刻，炎症物质正沿根管下行至根尖，从而造成牙根发炎，严重的短时间内就会出现局部肿胀、牙齿松动、不敢碰，等等。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">4</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">牙龈上长包、流脓，牙却不疼了</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>如果这时候，炎症物质破坏了根周围的骨头，就会穿破牙龈，形成“瘘管”。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>你的牙龈上会出现一个“小包包”——有木有？？</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>还会看见一些脓血流出来，有木有？？？</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>至此，牙持续性疼痛会暂时告一段落，如果不出现急性加重，可能你会觉得牙疼好了，你是不是以为你运气不坏啊，有木有？？？？</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>可如果没有出现瘘管，那炎症物质窝在根底下得不到引流，压力得不到释放，那种胀胀的疼痛可是不比急性期的牙髓炎轻多少哦。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>对了，此阶段很可能对热刺激很敏感，冷刺激无疼痛滴……</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="23" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section class="135brush" style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.39px;margin: 10px 0px; padding:15px 20px 15px 45px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); vertical-align: baseline; background-image: url(http://www.wx135.com/img/bg/left_quote.jpg); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); background-position: 1% 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;"><p style="color: inherit;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">上面说的是一般意义上的牙髓炎造成的疼痛及其发展过程，牙痛还有其它一些原因。</span></p></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">5</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">咬东西时突然疼一下，可能是牙隐裂</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>常见的牙疼原因有“牙隐裂”——多数人可能早期有要东西时咬到某一个位置时候会突然疼一下，很敏感的那种。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>有些经验不太丰富的医生会告诉你是牙齿过敏，于是你把能买到的脱敏牙膏几乎尝试了个便，可是问题也没有解决。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>相反，牙齿开始出现了冷热刺激疼，再往后，乖乖，看上面，复习一下，和“牙髓炎”一样哦。是的，再发展的确就是牙髓感染后那些症状。</p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xOKbSrIBGgib7B4xThEnaxkfzEGy58ZMjFeOdBT4K5eImgNWa1dtkicLVK0djiaVnOoSfHV46F9ZHumLUowoEibphw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5553359683794467" data-w=""><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">6</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">牙周炎牙疼，已经逆天啦</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>还有原因吗？这个——可以有！“牙周炎”也是常见的牙疼原因，只不过，它一般是发展到严重阶段，出现牙槽骨破坏后造成牙根外露，使内部牙髓受外界刺激引发的牙髓炎症。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>临床上把这类牙病叫“逆行性牙髓炎”。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">7</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">长智齿疼，“间歇性”发作</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>还有朋友说：“我长智齿了，也是牙疼！”——没错，有这种可能。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>长智齿时，一般智齿会压迫周围骨头引起不适。但是这种疼痛一般有“间歇性”发作的特点。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>还有，如果智齿斜着出来，可能会把前面的第7（从中间数第7颗牙，简称第7）顶坏，造成第7出现牙髓炎。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="29514" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="color: inherit;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; width: 1.8em; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); font-size: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);" data-width="1.8em"><section class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); color: inherit;">8</section></section></section><section style="margin: -1.56em 0px 1em 0.5em; padding: 0px; float: left; border-radius: 1em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); z-index: -1; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; float: left; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 2em; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;">后牙有缺损疼，横着刷牙造成的</span></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p>年龄大一点的朋友可能还会遇到另外一种情况。在口角区以后的“后牙颊侧”，靠近牙龈的边缘有一道“沟”状的缺损，深的话，刷牙、喝水也会疼。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>请注意了，有这种情况的朋友，请你们检讨一下自己的刷牙姿势。这个缺损临床上叫“楔状缺损”，它多见于刷牙姿势不正确。对！——横刷牙造成的！！</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>有不适的原因是缺损过深接近刺激了牙髓引起的疼痛。这个部位可是牙齿整体上距离牙髓最近的地方。发展下去也是“牙髓炎”的那几步。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="85660" class="135editor" style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px;" data-color="rgb(239, 112, 96)" data-custom="rgb(239, 112, 96)"><section style="margin-top: 2em; padding: 0.5em 0px; white-space: normal; border-style: solid none; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(166, 166, 166); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);"><section style="margin-top: -1.2em; text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: none; line-height: 1.4; color: inherit;"><span class="135brush" data-brushtype="text" style="border-color: rgb(241, 201, 196); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; padding: 8px 23px; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);">小结</span></section><section class="135brush" data-style="white-space: normal; text-align: left;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);" style="padding: 16px 16px 10px; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;"><p>说到这里，大家可能都清楚了，无论你的牙齿是出于什么损害，最后一般都是归结到“牙髓炎”——“根尖周炎”这样一个过程。正所谓“条条大路通罗马，神马都是牙髓炎”啊。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>另外，在跟医生描述牙疼的时候，你需要具体说明的除了牙位（哪一颗牙）以外，还要包括以下几点：有无冷热疼、自发疼、触碰疼，有无松动、肿胀，有无咬东西疼，等等！</p></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">您是否纠结怀孕和牙齿的问题，关注「好大夫在线」微信公众号，对话框回复<span style="font-size: 18px;">「<strong>怀孕看牙</strong>」</span>获取文章——《怀孕期间可以治疗牙疼吗》</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">责任编辑：不咸<br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">图片已购买版权</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">更多大专家的小建议，靠谱、实用！</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">关注「好大夫在线」微信公众号：<span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>haodf_wx</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xOKbSrIBGgib7B4xThEnaxkfzEGy58ZMjqeaqIk8uh0BWtgkD5SpL8nRH4wockeypNNhfAsWM0OX8DTFRmlUicTQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5422222222222223" data-w="450"><br></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">点击阅读原文进入陈宁医生个人网站！</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">↓↓↓↓</span></p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xOKbSrIBGgibbrDm4Eys9dSAy8lVyhPVAU9OfdjLBwvnps6jnph9WKVZW34yZQ6VL2GPxKUWYRloGXvFCbt1fEA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '21', '53', '-1', 0.05, '2015-08-02'),
(34, '0', '《十二道锋味》“卖萌担当”陈伟霆获封“正能量男神” 录制锋味最大感受：原来我真的是黑暗料理王', '<p>\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBQkDLjWBaC1esDj7WCeJuP5GAOicPc3gIVBlsEpGZjB1Hd3XOAM3IgbibPqia2aqYPbNPpzqM4D7sFmA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#999999;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	“当红小鲜肉”希望通过作品让粉丝看到内在的自己：偶像派也需要演技好吗？<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBQT2TRfvM1mXFNicbCMWhJckkZOoibiadG2FCphnlmEf3bECnXpvzia1L5q3XzPMo6apnJnp3Gfz9I3Pw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong> “大师兄”变身“小表弟”。浙江卫视《十二道锋味》第二季播出仅两期，当红小鲜肉陈伟霆已经成为“锋味家族”里的卖萌担当啦！观众连连点赞：乖巧、务实、嘴甜，不做作，优点简直一千个都说不完。<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>在节目里负责砍柴的陈伟霆，因为这样一段话更获得“正能量男神”的美誉——“好重啊那些柴，但是我觉得，因为后辈嘛，不可以在前辈面前有累的感觉。其实我觉得他们让我做什么我一定用全力，把我所有的能力去做好给大家看，因为毕竟我觉得自己的贡献有限，所以我觉得他们交给我的任务我就想办法去完成，这是我最基本对自己的要求。”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong> 12日，陈伟霆通过微信接受了全国媒体微信采访。这位一路打拼的年轻人，在分享自己的感受时，处处都能让人感受到他的谦逊和可爱。“当红小鲜肉”也不满足于享受当下的耀眼光环，他希望通过更多的作品，让粉丝看到陈伟霆的内在，而不仅是颜值。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#999999;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">“黑暗料理王”自认做饭没天分霆锋不仅教他做饭，还教他打咏春拳呢</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="p1">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="p1">\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBQT2TRfvM1mXFNicbCMWhJckDK4VGdBtpr8RBw313Fy9rhg375eCyHFfOpMF5Nq70f6hibrJDHOUu7g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>在此前的第二季《十二道锋味》发布会上，做菜基本属于零经验值的“泡面王子”伟霆，就被霆锋吐槽把干辣椒烧成了死蟑螂的模样，他也自认做的料理比“荔枝蘸酱汁还要黑暗”，连担任财务的马苏也“老是要看着他，生怕破坏了东西”，所以陈伟霆最后只能负责体力活：砍柴、备柴。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>谈及上《十二道锋味》最大的感受，伟霆笑着说：“最大的感受就是，原来我是真的黑暗料理王，对做饭方面完全没有天分，但是通过后面几个月的练习，后面也会自己做菜，肯定比之前好。但是是不是真的能做菜呢，我觉得还不行啊。”不过，随后的节目中还预埋了一个温情的“神秘包袱”：“以前就是个从来不会做菜的那种人，所以在《十二道锋味》里面，真的是我第一次做饭给我一个重要的人吃。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>聊到做菜，伟霆表示自己还是比较喜欢做西餐的感觉，“因为我妈妈就是每一天都吃西餐，为了我们才做那些广东菜，煲一些汤给我们”，他还透露，妈妈每天都在问这个节目。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>作为同门师兄弟，谈起和师兄霆锋私下相处时，伟霆爆料：“我们平时也有见面，有时间也会一起吃饭，不是在《十二道锋味》里他才教我一些东西。在前一年，他已经开始教我咏春拳，当然我现在的咏春拳也打不过他。”论做菜，当然是霆锋厉害。身为小师弟，有没有在节目中教霆锋跳舞吗？他回答：“我尝试过教他跳舞，但是他不愿意哦哈哈哈哈”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#999999;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">“偶像派也需要演技好吗”“当红小鲜肉”不满于当下的自己</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBQT2TRfvM1mXFNicbCMWhJckibrRxppEHkUx3Zq42ITEicI5CcWOlDvM9KeF1r0RDa9iaJgnzmfNwJKqg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>节目中，陈伟霆有聊到这样一段成长心路：自己在香港以歌手出道，但到了内地之后发现世界原来很宽广。这一两年间，事业迎来爆发期的陈伟霆，可谓四面开花，他说，“原来内地市场拍戏的团队真的很专业，也给我一些创新的感觉。”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>从“万年新人王”到“国民大师兄”，陈伟霆今年已经出道12年了，他说：“当然，这12年里面，有四五年都是在等的，都是没工作的，所以我觉得，真正我事业的开始可能就是五六年吧。当然上一年是我拿到的机会最大的，所以接下来也有很长的路等我我去挑战。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>采访中，陈伟霆特别提到了在拍摄电影巨制《大轰炸》的时候，身为前辈的刘烨和他分享的“娱乐圈生存技巧”，“他有跟我说教我好好做一个演员，演员就要做好自己的工作，喜欢演戏，因为这个是实力的表现嘛。可能大家很多人都会说‘小鲜肉’这样的名字，但是可能过一年两年之后，又会有新的小鲜肉，那我可以在哪里呢？就必须有作品，作品怎么才能支撑着我继续向前走？一个演员必须有实力，人家才会用你，不是因为你的热度。他（刘烨）跟我说，不能满足现在你拥有的，要赶紧改变自己，或者让大家看到里面的陈伟霆是什么。”当记者问觉得他和刘烨比谁更帅，他毫不犹豫回答，“当然是他比较帅了，除了外形好之后，内在的气场必须要靠累积才有的。所以，没法比。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>当大家问是不是正在苦练演技，打算完成偶像派向实力派的转型时，他笑着反问一句：“偶像派也需要演技好吗？”因为古装剧爆红的陈伟霆说，古装戏对他来说其实挑战挺大的，“我自己真的根本就是个现代人嘛，去演古装，很难走心。还有就是服装造型都很厚，也通常都是在夏天拍，对身体的挑战是很大的，因为会很热。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>身为“正能量男神”，陈伟霆如今在作品选择方面，也会特别在意小粉丝们的感受，“以前可能真的有一些比较大胆的戏，激情戏也好，古惑仔也好，但是现在真的有一些粉丝是年纪比较小的，比较忠诚跟着我的粉丝，我就会怕，会比较小心选择一些角色，还是多拍一些正能量一点的。我可以做反派，但不能太过的那种，我担心他们会学。等他们再长大一些的时候，我再拍一些挑战底线的戏吧。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> <strong><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="line-height:23.7999992370605px;"> </span></strong>作为一个贴心的偶像，在出道12周年之际，陈伟霆还推出了Plan W。关于这个项目，他解释道：“Plan W是我这个专辑，还有我关于所有音乐事宜的一个计划，预计10月或者11月就会开始出来，会维持至少一年多的时间，中间会不断推出一些作品，专辑、MV、还有跳舞的片段。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBR63xxicPSFV4VlOj7lF6mDwDibDPbLTDL8XlTiagia7Df03hQoptOFT4XmLLXGMBINictBKPbfdn6sC6g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#1F497D;">特别提示：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:left;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#1F497D;">【浙江卫视《十二道锋味》每周六晚22:00 美味开播】</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaFGEHxjZkBSBu7rD24xT4T2huNRfUCAicwG9MF52vZsdlgicsz0yAibicL3L4ENpFaVyLtNw2ic90qBElVtXk0mMCIw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '28', '1', '-1', 0.05, '2015-8-17');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `top`, `title`, `content`, `pic`, `type`, `pv`, `pv_max`, `money`, `day`) VALUES
(32, '0', '使用身份证复印件，不加这几个字，可能倾家荡产！', '<p><strong style="white-space: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(216, 40, 33); font-size: 15px; border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/m2DCjMCJD7bTnJUWIvFEw9FHnH6TNl56QDYzIlFM6YER8niaBWMGBXDianibsmT9rcGQIqkfDnO4NG3DZ3Vzib7GqQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5" width="auto" data-type="gif" data-ratio="0.23770491803278687" data-w="122" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">点击上方"</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 73, 125); border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">陕癫侠</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">"关注我</span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16.36px; line-height: 1.75em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="rich_media_thumb" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/RCFpsDTJibeGCpegicAAnAb0nhkkKS7icCoBkt54MBN2qxsuWOsVqq9X0pEMA7Q8hZ87jmTcXnUnaws33OPFbfjEg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5" width="auto" data-w="" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px; width: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important;"></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当您把自己的身份证复印件给别人时，你注意到过没有，要正确使用身份证复印件，保护好自己。否则，忽视会酿大祸！</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">下面的事情一定要起警惕。一个警察，听他说过，他们接到 一女士报案，说是别墅被卖掉了。后来一查发现，她把身份证复印件交给过中介，他们就是用复印件伪造了正本把人家的房子给骗了，中介找不到了。身份证附件给别人的时候自己一定要在上面签字。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有时难免要将身份证复印件交予他人如购车，保险。等等，以下是在司法部上班的朋友转寄的。供大家参考。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">身份证复印件正确签注写法如下</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">身份证复印件记得要签注写法是分三行</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">仅提供XX银行--------------</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">申请XX基金扣帐-----------</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他用无效-----------------------</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">注意：</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1、用蓝色笔。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2、部分笔画与身份证的字交叉或接触。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3、每一行后面一定要划上横线，以免被偷加其它文字。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4、上述文字一定要签在身份证的范围内，但不要遮住(身份证上的姓名、文字及号码)。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">无论是信用卡、基金、手机、申请书，只要须附身份证复印件的，或填写和身份证有类似作用的表格，一律照此办理。另外，对各类申请书内尚未填写的空格，如：附卡申请，加买保险，加买第二支基金，申请手机号等等，这些空格都必须打上，以免被不法业者补填它用。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这个真的是非常重要，如果你学习过相关法律课程或票据课程你就知道，所以大家一定要十分小心点，在身份证复印件上千万记得要签名哟！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">兹提供生活上便利的小方法保障自已的权利，你拿身份证复印件去办信用卡，记得在复印件上写：[此身份证复印件，仅为申请XX银行XX信用卡用，不得转为其它用途]。XXX签名。</span></strong></p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/OMdbYclvCbuZiaJtOpHRZAQcnnuqpaSD5dOobngaU8Rib5CoUWJVwAdzPaQAOvjeib3nKOTBqnAicpOmzmVDWA5fog/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '34', '50', '', 0.05, '2015-8-05'),
