F8500;">meibaifuhu</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">分享女性美白、祛斑、保湿、控油、祛痘、防晒等女性最喜欢的美容护肤小窍门.爱美就是爱自己,每个女孩都是独一无二的天使.</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;">女人处世智慧</span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">nvrenwisdom</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="color:#595959;">学做一个沉稳，细心，大度，有胆识的智慧女人，漂亮是天生的,智慧却是可以培养的！加关注,修炼气质，做个有气质的智慧女人！</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;">创意家居装修</span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">gz6680</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="color:#595959;">我想有个家,一个不需要太大的地方,家里的一砖一瓦都是我梦想的样子~~</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;"><strong>教你排毒养颜</strong></span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">adiphone</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">毒素使人生病,毒素使人变笨,毒素使人变丑,毒素使人衰老!排毒,排毒,刻不容缓!！</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;"><strong>教你扎头发</strong></span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">tiethehair</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">发型对了,怎么穿都美!爱折腾头发就关注我吧!</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;">女人私密话</span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">secretnvren</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">不做需要男人的女人，而做男人需要的女人。关注@女人私密话！掌握男女的那些事儿。</span><span style="color:#000000;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>女人要懂的那些事</strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">nvrensomething</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">没有丑女人，只有懒女人！关注@女人要懂的那些事，每天漂亮一点点!</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;">女人读心术</span></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">nvrenduxinshu</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">做个说话有心眼，办事有心计的女人，能让你轻松游走于男人的世界。猛点关注@女人读心术，教你一眼看透男人心</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><strong>减肥挺简单</strong></strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7C1414;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#D3D23F;">微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#D8D8D8;"><strong><span style="color:#FF8500;">jianfeiloss</span></strong></span><span style="color:#D3D23F;">（←长按复制）</span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;">瘦大腿、瘦小腿、瘦手臂，能瘦的地方都能瘦；瘦肚子，瘦脸，瘦腰，给予你的瘦身专业意见，30天拥有完美身材，屌爆了。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;"><span style="font-size:medium;line-height:27.9861125946045px;color:#FF8500;"><strong>如何关注：</strong></span><span style="font-size:medium;line-height:27.9861125946045px;color:#0C0C0C;">长按微信号复制 <strong><span style="color:#000000;line-height:27.9861125946045px;">&gt;</span></strong> 通讯录 <strong><span style="color:#000000;line-height:27.9861125946045px;">&gt;</span></strong> 添加朋友</span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#0C0C0C;font-size:medium;line-height:27.9861125946045px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#595959;"><span style="color:#333333;font-size:medium;line-height:27.9861125946045px;">以上是小编为大家挑选的最火的微信，不同类型，不同内容，希望给你的生活添加别样的风采！</span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/5QMWic0mIjPLNh926iabK1ppts9jgJL0icHJY7d7piauFNLSH5pc5VEzdcZRzpSSgo4DdVtKL40ogOwtspZORkvO1A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '22', '0', '-1', 0.05, '2015-8-17');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `top`, `title`, `content`, `pic`, `type`, `pv`, `pv_max`, `money`, `day`) VALUES
(69, '0', '减肥别忘了你的“大”脸！做个小脸美人！', '<p style="font-size:15.5555562973022px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Helvetica, 宋体;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#A5A5A5;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;">近期在日本风靡的八步按摩脸部减肉法，据说不用动刀就能够塑造出这样的V型脸，赶紧试试吧！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">真幸运，</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">在茫茫爱美之人中遇见你</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6IK1eGcarkIv3EabUBuwEqf9AmEBvrSfQf3qxNcZibWSMI95GHfibhKgg/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第一步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">由下巴开始，由外向内画圈至人中</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6FK7249qhnuVrPsKAfDQTYMscTSZ3va3RGTCcDREXrdNcZSNGcWGvDg/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第二步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">用手掌，从下巴开始向上提拉至耳侧</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6v7p94I37nibtbsbXyFibMKEzcfp9fSdH1TS7EFiarNNh7gwK3zVOBg7vw/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">｜第三步｜</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">用手掌沿着鼻翼两侧向上推至眼眶下，</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">接而从太阳穴沿着耳侧向下按摩</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6slx3Ue6AxYUP7KbkibiayzoLdQw5vIsvUjpjuVHaQCQbmxgOo6IfHQ6Q/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第四步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">用食指从人中开始向两侧提拉</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8xCf8yDDiaXk7aNNEqsUaHRFPp8FdiaNjBQ4HbYeMbWFgdsq3MGQW37Lkic3r1VvibICJwO65vY2JicrmDTGXkE9EdQ/640?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第五步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">用整双手提拉两侧脸蛋</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6J7HPfxzX1VcV0UhUr3R8YPOByP9oJSmJviabygAgwDtADaC2ia5kVGag/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第六步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">沿着颧骨上缘从眼尾开始向中间推，</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">接着沿着鼻梁向上按摩</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny6tXoI5S4xc2bhW9KsjNicI0g34fkcw12icGib1MjGEUfWkmT0DriaibEmhoQ/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第七步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">在眼睛下方，画8字按摩</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/f1ZibqSNprNlQTLSB3Op3m2zicDAGL7Ny69Mx4HcAQIiaO21UDT7u4OgM4ON0vAmJicicMjfuEmfXHMAuzOM7NQdxXA/0?wx_fmt=gif" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong><span style="color:#205867;">| 第八步 | </span></strong><strong><span style="color:#205867;">从鼻翼两侧沿着颧骨下方向两边提拉</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-family:sans-serif;text-indent:2em;">\r\n	<span style="color:#C0504D;font-family:微软雅黑;"><strong>最后，要提醒大家：瘦脸的同时要保护好肌肤啊！<span style="line-height:1.6em;">按摩时，要对脸部肌肤要温柔，切记过度摩擦，尽量手法要轻。</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style="font-size:15.5555562973022px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Helvetica, 宋体;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#A5A5A5;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:15.5555562973022px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Helvetica, 宋体;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#A5A5A5;">(本文内容来源于网络 版权归原作者所有)</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#1F497D;"><strong><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/17MiccsGRV0D2LfqIJGaG0SdOrQ3Ebl0BZmSDrMLia8x0UgcCzQDzkNrSuo7FfOQUkMbYHVvNYDtbv4YicqvaQl6w/640" width="auto" style="width:auto !important;" /></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#1F497D;"><strong>有人用微信聊天，有人却在微信中每天学习，自我成长。今