!important;" /></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>有人用微信聊天，有人却在微信中每天学习，自我成长。今天给大家推荐一些优质的微信公众号，每天成长一点点。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#FF0000;"><strong>长按黄色区域的微信号</strong></span><strong>，选择最上方“复制”标志，然后在 通讯录--添加 中粘贴并搜索关注。从指尖轻触开始，轻松搞定你的最爱！</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>学瑜伽练好身材</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span>微信号：</span><span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">ty9080</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">每日教你一招简单瑜伽动作，让你轻松瘦身，保持苗条身材。</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>教您一周瘦2斤</strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">mlk011</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">教您瘦大腿、瘦小腿、瘦手臂,能瘦的地方都能瘦;瘦肚子,瘦脸,瘦腰,一对一给予你健康的瘦身专业意见,30天拥有完美身材,一周瘦两斤.</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>美美搭</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">dab666</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">你说自己胖，个子矮，大脸又腿粗；你说变美很辛苦，需要不断付出； 我说矮个穿短款，粗腿靠九分紧身裤；我说变美很容易，只要你关注！ 美美搭，为你找寻美丽的出路！</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>教你扎头发</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">jjzy80</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">发型对了,怎么穿都美!爱折腾头发就关注我吧!每天教你如何弄头发。</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>心情说</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">xqshuo</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">每天心情即时更新;总有一句是为你而写;关注的时候你会发现有些心情读着读着你就哭了…</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>教你穿衣打扮</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">jnchuanyi</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">三分长相,七分打扮,爱时尚,爱美丽从穿衣开始!!!</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>轻松学瘦腿</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">ydl011</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:15px;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">美不美,先瘦腿,脸大不是病,粗腿要人命,关注“轻松学瘦腿”,教你拥有完美腿型~!</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>教你做菜</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">jnxzc8</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">做遍天下美食;尝尽人间美味——美食菜谱;你值得拥有!</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>教你美白祛斑</strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">sjyx80</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">雀斑、黄褐斑、妊辰斑，油脂粒、晒斑、黑头,痘印青春痘、半个月消除!教你健康,有效美白和祛斑方法,你不再为美丽而苦恼!</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>魅力女王说话术</strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#00A6BF;">微信号：<span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">shuohuanvwang</span></span><span style="color:#00A6BF;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">（←长按复制）</span></span> \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#F1F1F1;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">口才并不是一种天赋的才能，它是靠刻苦训练得来的！每天学点社交口才汇聚正能量，打造成别人眼中最具魅力、最有品位的魅力女王！</span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>疗伤话</strong></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote style="font-size:15px;color:#7C1414;font-family:微软雅黑;bac