(143, '0', '猎奇 | 如果你觉得我奇怪', '<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10px;color:#7F7F7F;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10px;color:#7F7F7F;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">搞艺术的都那样...</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">做设计的都那样...</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">玩儿音乐的都那样...</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;"><strong>blabla...</strong><strong></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="color:#7F7F7F;font-size:14px;">我就想问问你，哪！样！啊？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fm5MM2xCLo2ich4OkkC8leOevyXiaSNDdCenNSRx2fuFG3avyCK1acuJicHyvvKsNa82s6ezwHIIsyhaZJbuUy0mg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">我承认</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">活自己机率小的可以</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">活得像自己也是少数</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">“<span style="font-size:14px;color:#7F7F7F;">勇敢</span>”没全占</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;color:#7F7F7F;">也算是占了个“<span style="font-size:14px;color:#7F7F7F;">敢</span>”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fm5MM2xCLo2ich4OkkC8leOevyXiaSNDdCc