(196, '0', '扩散！这个东西已害死很多人……你也有！', '<p><strong style=""><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/C1qzkKYWX4Eiakj6bvibic10w4ia2Ivlwfic1EE4YIyZ8TjM7z96eM7Az20Aib7dJrdiaa7tZIGNzG6Dz4nvpoOd7ldsg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5059288537549407" data-w="" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></strong></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-id="126" data-color="rgb(172, 29, 16)" data-custom="rgb(172, 29, 16)" style=""><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: -0.8em 0.1em -0.8em 0.2em; padding: 0.8em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); border-top-left-radius: 0.3em; border-top-right-radius: 0.3em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.3em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">导语：</span></strong>过马路玩手机、开车等红灯时刷微博、看微信等行为屡见不鲜，“手机低头族”逐渐成为道路交通安全新隐患，而由此引发的车祸也在不断增加，“手机依赖症”带来的安全隐患值得每一位市民注意。小编在此提醒广大市民，行走在马路上切勿再做“低头族”，疏于观察路况很容易发生交通意外。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为了自己、为了他人！提醒身边所有人！</span></strong></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="1.5em" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 15.994318008422852px; width: 1.5em; float: left; border-width: 0px 0px 6px 6px; border-style: none none solid solid; border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="1.5em" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 15.994318008422852px; width: 1.5em; float: right; border-width: 0px 6px 6px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section><section data-width="0px" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><section class="135editor" data-id="85738" data-color="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-custom="rgb(33, 33, 34)" style=""><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 670px; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="70%" style="margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; width: 457.79827880859375px; float: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2015年8月22日</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">痛惜！5岁女孩过马路被公交车撞死 母亲当场哭晕…</span></strong></p></section></section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="0px" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="">8月22日晚，四川攀枝花一5岁女孩和母亲回家时，独自跑到公路上，被一辆公交车撞倒碾压身亡，母亲痛哭晕厥。有目击者称，当时母亲在看手机，没注意孩子，孩子独自跑到了马路上…再次提醒家长，出门请放下手机，看好孩子！（来自：人民日报——华西都市报）</p>\n<p style=""><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia40DvbrjVea1OgTdLyjTcvyJyEBqxMf1aCuianicjQZFZHOZl4jIObic0fA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.585" data-w="400" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-id="85738" data-color="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-custom="rgb(33, 33, 34)" style=""><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 670px; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="70%" style="margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; width: 457.79827880859375px; float: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2015年8月21日</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">妈妈看手机的工夫 儿子被轧身亡</span></strong></p></section></section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="0px" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="">8月21日下午，郑州某商场楼下，一2岁男童玩耍时被一驶离停车场的轿车碾压，抢救无效死亡。肇事司机已被带走调查。目击者称，孩子妈妈出事前正看手机，不在身边，一会儿工夫，孩子跑到了车辆右前轮位置…（来自：人民日报）</p>\n<p style=""><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia4TiaHknkESawvJBoQmgAeyFwd3w0SNLoQqqHhrWzhPCOuZmiaACMfaoWg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="440" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-id="85738" data-color="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-custom="rgb(33, 33, 34)" style=""><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 670px; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="70%" style="margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; width: 457.79827880859375px; float: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2015年8月21日</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 129, 189); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一轿车失控冲上公交站台 撞伤5人</span></strong></p></section></section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="0px" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="">8月21日中午13:04，南京岳某驾驶轿车，由西向东行驶到定淮门大街舸舫西园附近时，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">因为低头捡滑落的手机，</span></strong>导致车辆方向失控，撞上公交站台，5人被撞伤，其中3人骨折。目前肇事司机已经被控制。（来自：现代快报）</p>\n<p style=""><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia4suXqp7eb0LndDHVmaic8ywLibnL2H4mia41f3ZfvpCnjLHjUj6dkxApOw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.1318181818181818" data-w="440" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-id="85738" data-color="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-custom="rgb(33, 33, 34)" style=""><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 