mportant;"></p>\n<p style="">据羊城晚报，5月31日下午，广东中山，一名年轻女子右手接听手机，当她横过马路时，出现在其右边的一辆白色货车迅速将其撞倒在地，随即又被迎面而来的一辆泥头车辗压过去。目击者称，车祸现场非常惨烈。有网友表示，货车也没有减速。低头族，别再“玩命”了！（来自：人民日报）</p>\n<p style=""><img data-type="gif" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia4IyQ0IRrBOdIeK42NF0A2EbX1mPp3AR9oXSxib6XcX7F7P2sBv0n2GqA/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="320" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style=""><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vRaVWGC0F61icMicO11to0xj8Sgfdoexia4bguydApZX2x0tamxv52XlmPSSXXqWJqoG33dRic7n9RM9b2ozwZhqFg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.0275" data-w="400" width="auto" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style=""><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section class="135editor" data-id="71382" data-color="rgb(172, 29, 16)" data-custom="rgb(172, 29, 16)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; line-height: 22.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="135brush" data-style="background-color:rgb(33, 33, 34); border-bottom-left-radius:0px; border-bottom-right-radius:0em; border-top-left-radius:0px; border-top-right-radius:0em; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(255, 255, 255); display:block; font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em; text-align:center;padding:0px 15px;" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-wi